  p We have no control over, and assume no responsibility for the content, privacy policies or practices of any third party sites, products or services.

  h3 Cookies
  p To enrich and perfect your online experience, Radical Insight may use "Cookies", similar technologies and services provided by others to display personalized content, appropriate advertising and store your preferences on your computer.
  p A cookie is a string of information that a website stores on a visitor's computer, and that the visitor's browser provides to the website each time the visitor returns. Radical Insight uses cookies to help Radical Insight identify and track visitors, their usage of http://www.rad-insight.com, and their website access preferences. Radical Insight visitors who do not wish to have cookies placed on their computers should set their browsers to refuse cookies before using Radical Insight's websites, with the drawback that certain features of Radical Insight's websites may not function properly without the aid of cookies.
  p By continuing to navigate our website without changing your cookie settings, you hereby acknowledge and agree to Radical Insight's use of cookies.

